   A man was killed when a car burst into flames on the Durban M4. Video: Crisis Medical Services 
  
 

Crisis Medical Services reported to the scene and said there was nothing paramedics could do. 
“Unfortunately there was nothing paramedics could do to assist and the single occupant of the vehicle was declared deceased on the scene. The scene was secured and handed over to the South African Police Services for further investigation and processing,” said Kyle van Reenen, a spokesperson for Crisis Medical.
